14:58.292 --> 14:59.918
- Sold! Will you
- take a check?

15:01.417 --> 15:03.147
(SNORTING) As part of

15:03.148 --> 15:04.876
your perfect boyfriend

15:01.417 --> 15:04.876
package,

15:04.918 --> 15:06.730
may I present

15:06.731 --> 15:08.542
a romantic candlelit

15:04.918 --> 15:08.542
dinner?

15:10.375 --> 15:11.584
Is that extra?

15:11.585 --> 15:12.792
Because I kind of spent

15:10.375 --> 15:12.792
