15:16.792 --> 15:19.083
(SCREAMING)

15:19.125 --> 15:20.792
Fire bad!

15:20.834 --> 15:22.292
Wait, wait.

15:27.292 --> 15:28.606
Why do my boyfriend's

15:28.607 --> 15:29.918
always run away from me?

15:29.959 --> 15:31.876
- How much time - do you have?
- (LAUGHING)

15:33.209 --> 15:34.417
(GRUNTING)

15:39.792 --> 15:40.814
Excuse me,

15:40.815 --> 15:41.834
Weinermeister...

15:41.876 --> 15:43.751
That's Burgermeister.

15:43.792 --> 15:44.918
The Weinermeister

15:44.919 --> 15:46.042
called in sick.

15:46.083 --> 15:47.876
Something about some plague,

15:47.877 --> 15:49.667
but I'm sure it's nothing.

15:50.250 --> 15:51.250
(GRUNTING)

15:52.667 --> 15:54.000
Well, pretty sure.

16:00.000 --> 16:02.000
I did not know

16:02.001 --> 16:04.000
this village had

16:00.000 --> 16:04.000
a Pumpkin Princess.

16:04.042 --> 16:05.667
Duh. Pumpkins can't

16:05.668 --> 16:07.292
just govern themselves.

16:07.334 --> 16:08.751
I'm going to let you

16:08.752 --> 16:10.167
think about what you

16:07.334 --> 16:10.167
just said.

16:12.083 --> 16:13.542
(CROWD SCREAMING)

